223
00:13:04,500 --> 00:13:06,375
- WHY WON'T YOU LEAVE ME ALONE?

224
00:13:06,458 --> 00:13:08,416
WHAT DO YOU CARE
IF I CRY OVER HIM?

225
00:13:09,375 --> 00:13:10,750
