226
00:13:10,833 --> 00:13:13,791
SO, STOP ACTING AS THOUGH
YOU GIVE A DAMN ABOUT IT.

227
00:13:13,875 --> 00:13:17,041
- WELL, AREN'T WE DADDY'S
SURLY LITTLE PRINCESS?

228
00:13:17,125 --> 00:13:18,208
LOOK, ALL I'M SAYING IS THAT

229
00:13:18,291 --> 00:13:19,750
YOU DON'T HAVE TO
BE MAGICALLY FINE

230
00:13:19,833 --> 00:13:22,125
WITH YOUR OLD MAN BEING GONE.

231
00:13:22,208 --> 00:13:23,458
YOU SHOULDN'T BE.

232
00:13:23,541 --> 00:13:24,958
AND WHATEVER
YOU'RE SADDLED WITH,

233
00:13:25,041 --> 00:13:27,916
SADNESS, DESPAIR, HATE,

234
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:31,250
HIT ME WITH IT. SERIOUSLY,
GIVE ME YOUR BEST SHOT.

235
00:13:31,333 --> 00:13:34,041
AFTER ALL, IT'S MY FAULT
YOU'RE FEELING IT.

236
00:13:36,291 --> 00:13:38,083
Akatsuki: I KILLED
YOUR DAD, MIU.

237
00:13:41,125 --> 00:13:42,875
IT MUST'VE BEEN SO SUDDEN.

238
00:13:42,958 --> 00:13:46,375
ONE DAY, HE'S ALIVE.
THE NEXT DAY, HE'S...

239
00:13:46,458 --> 00:13:50,083
BUT DON'T BOTTLE IT UP, OKAY?
BETTER JUST TO LET IT OUT.

240
00:13:50,708 --> 00:13:51,750
I MEAN IT.

241
00:13:54,500 --> 00:13:56,250
I'M NO FOOL, OKAY?

242
00:13:56,333 --> 00:13:58,625
I KNOW YOU COULD HATE ME
FOR WHAT I DID

243
00:13:58,708 --> 00:14:00,125
BUT I'M HERE
FOR YOU EITHER WAY.

244
00:14:00,750 --> 00:14:02,208
JUST KNOW THAT.

245
00:14:02,291 --> 00:14:04,666
IF YOU EVER NEED TO CRY,
BUT THE TEARS WON'T COME,

246
00:14:05,708 --> 00:14:07,166
I CAN MAKE IT SO THEY DO.

247
00:14:07,250 --> 00:14:09,000
AND NOBODY ELSE CAN DO THAT
FOR YOU RIGHT NOW.

248
00:14:09,083 --> 00:14:11,750
NOT EVEN YOURSELF.

249
00:14:11,833 --> 00:14:14,916
THAT'S WHY I TAPPED IN TO
YOUR TRUE FEELINGS JUST NOW.

250
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:18,708
YOU NEED A GOOD CRY, AND THIS
IS AS GOOD A TIME AS ANY.

251
00:14:21,958 --> 00:14:23,625
- ( Miu sobbing )

252
00:14:23,708 --> 00:14:26,125
- THAT'S IT.
JUST LET EVERYTHING OUT.

253
00:14:26,208 --> 00:14:28,708
I'M HERE FOR YOU
AND I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

254
