257
00:14:52,416 --> 00:14:56,291
I MEAN, THEY'RE
SO HUGE ALREADY. JEEZ.

258
00:14:56,375 --> 00:14:57,583
- ( she sighs )

259
00:14:57,666 --> 00:14:59,291
- I'LL MAKE THE PERV TAKE
ME CLOTHES SHOPPING

260
00:14:59,375 --> 00:15:01,416
NEXT TIME WE GET A DAY OFF.

261
