262
00:15:09,208 --> 00:15:12,291
MAYBE I'D BETTER HAVE KUZUHA
AND IZUMI TAKE ME INSTEAD.

263
00:15:12,375 --> 00:15:14,000
- Akatsuki: LET ME GUESS.
SHOPPING TRIP?

264
00:15:14,083 --> 00:15:15,583
- YEAH.

265
00:15:15,666 --> 00:15:18,333
I JUST HOPE YOUR WORLD HAS
TOPS THAT'LL ACTUALLY FIT ME.

266
00:15:25,583 --> 00:15:27,125
- OH, DON'T MIND ME.

267
00:15:27,208 --> 00:15:30,916
I'M JUST KNOCKING OUT ONE OF MY
ENERGY MANIPULATION EXERCISES.

268
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:33,833
FOR THIS PARTICULAR ONE,
YOU SEND ENERGY INTO YOUR FEET

269
00:15:33,916 --> 00:15:35,291
AND USE IT TO STAND
PERPENDICULAR

270
00:15:35,375 --> 00:15:36,916
TO A VERTICAL SURFACE.

271
