- ( Miu screaming )

272
00:15:51,375 --> 00:15:53,750
Newscaster: IN OTHER NEWS,
THE UPCOMING G7 SUMMIT

273
00:15:53,833 --> 00:15:55,666
SCHEDULED FOR
THE IMPERIAL PALACE...

274
00:15:55,750 --> 00:15:59,708
- Miu: I KNOW HE WAS UP THERE
FIRST AND ALL, BUT STILL...

275
00:15:59,791 --> 00:16:02,375
WOULD IT HAVE KILLED HIM TO SAY
SOMETHING BEFORE I WAS NAKED?

276
00:16:02,458 --> 00:16:03,666
- Newscaster: ATTENDEES
FROM ARRIVING IN JAPAN,

277
00:16:03,750 --> 00:16:07,041
