YOU'RE HUNG UP ON HIM.

358
00:19:31,041 --> 00:19:32,166
- HUNG UP HOW?

359
00:19:32,250 --> 00:19:33,958
- I JUST MEAN THEY CAN'T
STICK YOU IN A HOUSE

360
