WITH THIS RIPPED YOUNG HOTTIE,

361
00:19:35,916 --> 00:19:37,791
AND THEN TELL YOU THAT
YOU'RE BROTHER AND SISTER

362
00:19:37,875 --> 00:19:39,916
AND EXPECT YOU
TO FEEL A FAMILY BOND.

363
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:42,083
