389
00:20:35,958 --> 00:20:37,083
IT'D NEVER WORK OUT.

390
00:20:43,666 --> 00:20:44,791
- THE GUY ON THE PLANE.

391
00:20:47,166 --> 00:20:48,458
I'VE SEEN HIM BEFORE.

392
00:20:50,833 --> 00:20:51,791
- ( door opening )

393
00:20:53,250 --> 00:20:56,250
- OH! SOMEBODY BEAT ME
TO THE PUNCH.

394
