ON THE CAMPUS.

395
00:20:58,708 --> 00:21:01,083
WELL, SO MUCH FOR HAVING
IT ALL TO MYSELF, I GUESS.

396
00:21:02,500 --> 00:21:04,000
HUH.

397
00:21:04,083 --> 00:21:06,791
CALL ME CRAZY, BUT I FEEL LIKE
I'VE SEEN YOU SOMEWHERE BEFORE.

398
00:21:06,875 --> 00:21:10,166
NOT JUST IN PASSING, MIND YOU.
LIKE, I KNOW YOU FROM SOMEWHERE.

399
00:21:10,250 --> 00:21:11,958
I DON'T GUESS
THE FEELING IS MUTUAL?

400
00:21:12,041 --> 00:21:14,875
- LOOK, PAL. I DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU'RE GOING ON ABOUT, OKAY?

401
00:21:14,958 --> 00:21:16,625
MAYBE YOU GOT ME
CONFUSED WITH SOMEONE ELSE.

402
00:21:18,083 --> 00:21:19,791
- AH! I REMEMBER!

403
00:21:19,875 --> 00:21:22,791
THE NEW GUY, AKATSUKI
OUSAWA, THAT RIGHT?

404
00:21:22,875 --> 00:21:24,208
- YEAH, WHAT'S IT TO YOU?

405
00:21:24,291 --> 00:21:25,958
- ( he chuckles )
- FUNNY GUY.

406
00:21:26,041 --> 00:21:28,208
YOU KNOW YOU'RE ALL ANYONE
CAN TALK ABOUT LATELY.

407
00:21:28,291 --> 00:21:30,333
I READ UP ON YOUR LITTLE BRUSH
WITH THE STUDENT COUNCIL

408
00:21:30,416 --> 00:21:32,791
IN THE SCHOOL PAPER.

409
00:21:32,875 --> 00:21:34,208
PUT HER THERE!
WHAT DO YOU SAY?

410
00:21:38,541 --> 00:21:41,083
- SO, YOU KINDA FAIL AT
SHAKING HANDS THERE, BLONDIE.

411
