- ( theme music playing )

412
00:21:49,500 --> 00:21:50,958
- ( singing in Japanese )

413
00:23:19,416 --> 00:23:21,041
- Listy: FOR REASONS I CAN'T
BEGIN TO FATHOM,

414
00:23:21,125 --> 00:23:23,208
