SETS MY BLOOD ABOIL.

423
00:23:38,250 --> 00:23:40,875
I REALLY HOPE HE
GETS HIS COMEUPPANCE.

424
00:23:40,958 --> 00:23:43,750
NEXT EPISODE,
"JUST A SHORT REPOSE".

425
00:23:43,833 --> 00:23:45,000
